#. Tag: para
#: taskdependencyeditorlist.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view is not shown by default. For large projects, it can impact "
"performance severely"
msgstr ""
"Esta vista non se amosa de forma predeterminada. No caso de obxectos "
"grandes, pode reducir o rendemento de maneira significativa."

#. Tag: para
#: taskdependencyeditorlist.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It can be activated using the <link linkend=\"the-view-selector\">View "
"Selector</link> context menu."
msgstr ""
"Pode activarse coa entrada <link linkend=\"the-view-selector\">Ver o "
"selector</link> do menú contextual."
